highlights.text: Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #11.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 867 days straight.
“Vem No Galope” by AG031, MC Nito, and Dj Ph Da Vp is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 68 spots at #123.
